snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard: FIRE MEET GASOLINE
snippet.description: My favorite couple met each other almost seven years ago and they have been in a very serious relationship for at least four years. They got married in February-2015. The best definition for them is (and continues to be) fire and gasoline. They're really made for each other and their love seems to be an endless flame! God bless them and their love always!
tags: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Depp
